{"tid":2122691,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"1/3 公僕在家工作延至下月2日","createTime":"2020-07-24T06:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T06:45:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d7b61df681b9ca63f2a37d2f56184f9bf56c0d55","tid":2122691,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:45:41.000Z","msg":"1/3 公僕在家工作延至下月2日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/QXOBAXAI5Z6SCCY2DGPMYP3OB4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FQXOBAXAI5Z6SCCY2DGPMYP3OB4%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6BPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=b0d055ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FQXOBAXAI5Z6SCCY2DGPMYP3OB4%2F&h=d115f730\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200724/QXOBAXAI5Z6SCCY2DGPMYP3OB4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n公僕在家工作延至下月2日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CJnEoOombAs6IjPQBYPfG1Ez2YI=/190x142/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UKQEHSQMLLOXYERNWVVRVYWJDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCJnEoOombAs6IjPQBYPfG1Ez2YI%3D%2F190x142%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUKQEHSQMLLOXYERNWVVRVYWJDU.jpg&h=1bc80aee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前仍有約三分二公務員未能在家工作。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府宣佈因應疫情嚴峻，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：觀塘帝盛變隔離中心 住客急退房<br />\n<br />\n工會斥政府措施慢半拍<br />\n<br />\n公務員工會聯合會總幹事梁籌庭指出，目前仍有約三分二公務員未能在家工作，他認為統計部門及總務部的員工有較大空間在家工作，理應可再減少辦公室聚集的人流。第三波疫情至今，陸續有公務員及政府外判員工染疫，但政府本周一始安排公務員在家工作，被問到是否因政府遲安排所致，以及會否問責，食物及衞生局副局長徐德義未有正面回應，僅稱政府會密切觀察疫情發現，有需要時推出適當措施，公務員在家工作只是其中一個措施。<br />\n<br />\n梁籌庭就指無辦。。。。。。。。。"}]}